These images are a set of 17 bitmaps all of which are 24x24 pixels.
Web browsers should allow these bitmaps to join together to form boxes,
separators and 3d indentation lines. However having said this some web
browsers are brain dead with regard to images, and should be upgraded.
<P>

This is experimental only and may or may not remain in the WWW Images
Library. <P>

These images are courtesy of the Crossfire Developers. More box, and wall
style images can be found in
<A HREF="http://www.cit.gu.edu.au/~anthony/icons/" TARGET="_top">
Anthony's Icon Library </A>, under the section
``<A HREF="http://www.cit.gu.edu.au/~anthony/icons/prog/walls"
